{"tid":1614343,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"學術討論 點樣變身最安全","createTime":"2019-10-02T18:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T14:06:30.000Z","uid":3280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6d6bdafaf6cd67d1a83e75d79ac63719b09e2a","tid":1614343,"uid":3280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"要當正全天候俾CCTV影曬你做既野<br />\n（實際上週圍都有cam）<br />\n1. 係咪肯定全身無一樣野會俾人認到？<br />\n對鞋咩款？ 眼鏡？<br />\n你個背包？會唔會你未變身已經俾人影到用緊呢個款 變左身又係？<br />\n<br />\n2. 換裝地點最好要計劃定<br />\n舉個例子 你入左間餐廳變左身出返黎<br />\n餐廳出面有cam<br />\n要起底其實好易 對比返有咩人入左去無出返黎<br />\n<br />\n喺街度搵遮其實好差<br />\n有影曬換裝前後 <br />\n<br />\n建議做法：變身位有兩個出入口<br />\n儘量兩個位都無cam<br />\n仲要有街方出入"},{"pid":"b2465a376227d9e5597ae2997fdddeb5441ab18f","tid":1614343,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZ1GPbN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZ1GPbN.jpg&h=2767630d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8qo2wQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8qo2wQ.gif&h=e9ecabc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d39e4ae9c7e1312386981fafddc2f5caa5761ab","tid":1614343,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:10:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79192fa778cf822ca3f0a040bfccca9a6e8914d2","tid":1614343,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:14:24.000Z","msg":"搵公園嘅公厠換裝，有個app叫衝厠，可以睇埋地點距離，背囊就用背囊套套住"},{"pid":"78d4096a17de1f5311310e14d24f8997ebccf1f0","tid":1614343,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79192fa778cf822ca3f0a040bfccca9a6e8914d2","tid":1614343,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:14:24.000Z","msg":"搵公園嘅公厠換裝，有個app叫衝厠，可以睇埋地點距離，背囊就用背囊套套住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:14:40.000Z","msg":"公廁門口冇camp"},{"pid":"d2dd0708bb66ca096912d30b680c6e45a0aa7fa1","tid":1614343,"u